	dprr:hasNoteText "Dig. 11.5.2.1 and 3. Author of a law limiting wagers to contests virtutis causa. The date is uncertain but precedes 81 if the later Lex Cornelia was carried by Sulla. No title preserved. See Niccolini, FTP 433." .
